contentrichtext.text: {{italictitle}} {{Taxobox | name = ''Xeniaria truncata'' | image = | image_width = | image_caption = | regnum = [[Animal]]ia | phylum = [[Arthropod]]a | classis = [[Insect]]a | ordo = [[Earwig|Dermaptera]] | subordo = [[Arixeniina]] | familia = [[Arixeniidae]] | genus = [[Xeniaria]] | species = '''''X. truncata''''' | binomial = ''Xeniaria truncata'' | binomial_authority = Maa 1974 <ref name="ERC">http://earwigs-online.de/names.html</ref> }} '''''Xeniaria truncata''''' is a species of [[earwig]]s, in the genus Xeniaria, family Arixeniidae, the suborder Arixeniina, and the order [[Dermaptera]]. It is one of three genera in the genus Xeniaria. == References == {{reflist}} [[Category:Earwigs]] {{earwig-stub}}
